<section class="info-section">
	<div class="info-content">
		<div class="info-header">
			<svg class="info-icon" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
				<circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/>
				<line x1="12" y1="16" x2="12" y2="12"/>
				<line x1="12" y1="8" x2="12.01" y2="8"/>
			</svg>
			<h3>À savoir</h3>
		</div>
		<ul class="info-list">
			<li>
				<svg class="check-icon" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
					<polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/>
				</svg>
				<span>Hors période du Festival d'Avignon, les logements sont destinés prioritairement à la location meublée sous bail étudiant ou bail mobilité.</span>
			</li>
			<li>
				<svg class="check-icon" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
					<polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/>
				</svg>
				<span>Une caution émanant d'un tiers physique ou d'un organisme agréé (Visale, Garantme, Cautioneo) est requise lors de la constitution du dossier.</span>
			</li>
		</ul>
	</div>
</section>

<style>
	.info-section {
		margin: 3rem 0;
		padding: 0;
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f5f7fa 0%, #c3cfe2 100%);
		border-radius: 16px;
		overflow: hidden;
		box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
	}

	.info-content {
		max-width: 900px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		padding: 2.5rem;
		background: white;
		margin: 2rem;
		border-radius: 12px;
	}

	.info-header {
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 0.75rem;
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
		padding-bottom: 1rem;
		border-bottom: 2px solid #e0e7ff;
	}

	.info-icon {
		color: #667eea;
		flex-shrink: 0;
	}

	.info-content h3 {
		font-size: 1.5rem;
		margin: 0;
		color: #1a1a1a;
		font-weight: 600;
	}

	.info-list {
		list-style: none;
		padding: 0;
		margin: 0;
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 1.25rem;
	}

	.info-list li {
		display: flex;
		align-items: flex-start;
		gap: 1rem;
		font-size: 1.05rem;
		line-height: 1.7;
		color: #4a5568;
		padding: 1rem;
		background: #f8f9ff;
		border-radius: 8px;
		border-left: 3px solid #667eea;
		transition: all 0.2s ease;
	}

	.info-list li:hover {
		background: #f0f4ff;
		transform: translateX(4px);
	}

	.check-icon {
		color: #667eea;
		flex-shrink: 0;
		margin-top: 0.15rem;
	}

	.info-list li span {
		flex: 1;
	}

	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.info-content {
			padding: 1.5rem;
			margin: 1rem;
		}

		.info-header {
			margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
		}

		.info-content h3 {
			font-size: 1.25rem;
		}

		.info-list li {
			font-size: 0.95rem;
			padding: 0.875rem;
		}

		.check-icon {
			width: 18px;
			height: 18px;
		}
	}
</style>

